							<p class="lead">As summer fades and fall arrives in Stockton, it's the perfect time to prepare your fence for the cooler months ahead. While Stockton doesn't experience harsh winters like other regions, seasonal changes still impact fence materials and require proactive maintenance to prevent costly repairs and extend your fence's lifespan.</p>
							
